{"tid":361444,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Daniel Craig: 將出演第25集占士邦","createTime":"2017-08-16T06:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T08:07:24.000Z","uid":19113,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"180d7be2e905116d7288fe4229a15011578580da","tid":361444,"uid":19113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T06:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/143101_32572f77b1146dc76552a3a98ff79720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F143101_32572f77b1146dc76552a3a98ff79720.jpg&h=d9483e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為世界上其中一位最有品味的特務，James Bond 是很多演員夢寐以求出演的角色，但顯然觀眾還是很期待 Daniel Craig 的回歸，雖然昨日 Daniel Craig 在擔任 Boston 一個電台節目時親口說出了目前還未決定是否要再度出演 James Bond 一角：<br />\n<br />\nNo decision has been made at the moment, there&rsquo;s a lot of noise out there and nothing official has been confirmed and I&rsquo;m not, like, holding out for more money or doing anything like that. It&rsquo;s just all very personal decisions to be made at the moment&hellip;I know they&rsquo;re desperate to get going and I would in theory love to do it, but there is no decision, uh, just yet.<br />\n但他在隨後出席 Stephen Colbert 所主持的《The Late Show With Stephen Colbert》中，回應主持人提問會否再次出演 James Bond 時又肯定地回應說：「YES.」，雖然沒有其他的細節，但相信已教一眾《007》迷放下心頭大石了。Daniel Craig，歡迎回歸出演第 25 套《007》電影。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/colbertlateshow/status/897670453338267650\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcolbertlateshow%2Fstatus%2F897670453338267650&d=2ESWIHTXR5avICjTrTYw9p7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=168621d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcolbertlateshow%2Fstatus%2F897670453338267650&h=e3c8bd62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/colbertlateshow/status/897670453338267650</a>"},{"pid":"79480757fa4d94086a9e903564cde57af0dc55ba","tid":361444,"uid":18430,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T07:53:51.000Z","msg":"the best bond"},{"pid":"c3a8eb73decfa3752433cd505a8bb34db5ef295e","tid":361444,"uid":28619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:38:03.000Z","msg":"又唔知收左幾多億美金先肯拍<br />\n之前咬牙切齒話寧願死都唔拍<br />\n搵埋搵埋夠5，6代無憂無慮過日子"},{"pid":"2a9f3cdcadc7602afa514ca763126f48e5f23472","tid":361444,"uid":2545,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:41:23.000Z","msg":"想當年CAST佢拍第一集果陣唔知幾多百萬人屌佢又樣衰又唔型<br />\n宜家結果完全相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申我都係鍾意睇佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d26fda0cbbd36bc7ec7b4bf9366b01f0d152d04","tid":361444,"uid":36481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:42:44.000Z","msg":"正撚到仆街"},{"pid":"02506ab035d0af8e6b26fe3a48f0599dd28d45ef","tid":361444,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:43:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想當年CAST佢拍第一集果陣唔知幾多百萬人屌佢又樣衰又唔型<br />\n宜家結果完全相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申我都係鍾意睇佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太大隻，好似係咁講"},{"pid":"29a09fefa5c39f8af68353844b12e449b206984e","tid":361444,"uid":89301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:44:05.000Z","msg":"最似占士邦既男人"},{"pid":"abf799b2c7be570a6222fa896bca7708d369b62d","tid":361444,"uid":35112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想當年CAST佢拍第一集果陣唔知幾多百萬人屌佢又樣衰又唔型<br />\n宜家結果完全相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申我都係鍾意睇佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太大隻，好似係咁講</blockquote><br />\n似普京"},{"pid":"1e272843a43097fbc85967426415f76f0362b17e","tid":361444,"uid":98659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T12:0